{"tid":2054093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西威脅退出世衛組織","createTime":"2020-06-07T00:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T02:44:03.000Z","uid":28114,"like":85,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9cc57b4577367424f3c53a8a24020c6eb6841e0d","tid":2054093,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T00:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/0ad7a628-a83d-11ea-ab27-005056bf18d4/w:900/p:16x9/AP20146511970885.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.rfi.fr%2Fmedia%2Fdisplay%2F0ad7a628-a83d-11ea-ab27-005056bf18d4%2Fw%3A900%2Fp%3A16x9%2FAP20146511970885.jpg&h=d7cb3d26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴西總統博索納羅近照 &copy; AP - Eraldo Peres攝影<br />\n<br />\n巴西總統博索納羅在6月6日星期六表示，世界衛生組織懷有&ldquo;意識形態偏見&rdquo;，並威脅退出該組織。<br />\n<br />\n按照新冠病毒死亡人數來看，巴西目前排名世界第三。博索納羅指責世衛組織曾一度短暫地暫停了羥氯喹的臨床試驗。他表示：&ldquo;美國已經離開了世衛組織，巴西現在也在研究，未來離開世衛組織。要麼世衛組織能夠做到摒棄意識形態的偏見努力工作，要麼巴西也會離開&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n除了本周重啟羥氯喹的臨床實驗，世衛組織本周還改口建議人們普遍佩戴口罩。截至目前，新冠病毒在全世界已經造成將近40萬人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/國際/20200606-巴西威脅退出世衛組織\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F20200606-%E5%B7%B4%E8%A5%BF%E5%A8%81%E8%84%85%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%96%E8%A1%9B%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94&d=gQ7zj4J1baFceLD6a1UzUpuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=3a9cd585\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/國際/20200606-巴西威脅退出世衛組織</a>"},{"pid":"d8b52ee69fb81caaf3c7e5f6c27a4c7d37ef5ba0","tid":2054093,"uid":28114,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T00:52:38.000Z","msg":"退黨保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad45fece351801efcdacc647900082fb93b06eb","tid":2054093,"uid":8257,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"d8b52ee69fb81caaf3c7e5f6c27a4c7d37ef5ba0","tid":2054093,"uid":28114,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T00:52:38.000Z","msg":"退黨保平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},