093,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T01:10:45.000Z","msg":"國際組織的成立就係整合資料,再分析同建議<br />\n<br />\n因為小國根本撥唔出資源個各有各做,而且各有國做會有資源浪費同難於獲得別國資料<br />\n<br />\n跟世衛建議衰左可以賴世衛<br />\n唔跟世衛建議衰左(或提早鎖國重創經濟)就係自己問責<br />\n<br />\n<ins>我的立場係應該退會保平安,同時約埋美國台灣攪新大台</ins>"},{"pid":"c36ec320f3c5304027926cff05fc35a69bdae7ac","tid":2054093,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T01:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b8e0997320e0a32a41b685e19269b4a47094149","tid":2054093,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T01:27:55.000Z","msg":"快啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb59a999ae50864b29859f1088f370e7693abcc","tid":2054093,"uid":235174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T01:29:09.000Z","msg":"你地唔好開心住, 呢條友痴線wor"},{"pid":"3c2eea7dd7fa8c8f5a5a13101fe8aed05b394a7e","tid":2054093,"uid":59283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T01:30:37.000Z","msg":"呢個總統係無腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同侵美國唔妥WHO唔同"},{"pid":"9b48fbf5ec6b624f3744dae171a4d22e3718b5a3","tid":2054093,"uid":192465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T01:35:37.000Z","msg":"我有預感WW3同盟國 軸心國開始成型"},{"pid":"41e642853a387bd639738c9f786ed53a65d54cfe","tid":2054093,"uid":17103,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T01:40:57.000Z","msg":"日本韓國香港台灣早全世界 6 個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係四個都比中共既淫威壓逼, 真係戇鳩既命運"},{"pid":"f55863acdc1ee7ffcca868e99f6af6cd55cc927b","tid":2054093,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-0